name: Baby Names D to J
description:
Test Your Knowledge in D to J Baby Names using this app.

Learn about the best name that you can choose for your baby.

The database include more than 500 questions.

It only requires 1 minute of your time every day.

Answer 10 questions and increase your knowledge.

It is just another kind of app to choose how to "name my baby".

Compete against other players by scoring the highest score on the Leaderboard.
